metadata.name: Taking A Break
metadata.description:
Meet buddy.  He is one of the chillest good boy you will ever meet. Join buddy in his adventure around the world.

Buddy, is among the two giant dogs roaming the world looking for treats and good places to nap. I will introduce the other giant dog very soon, till then , sit back and relax and if things get a little too much in your life , buddy is here to calm your nerves.
